Example
Create a trait and use it in a class:
<?php
trait message1 {
public function msg1() {
echo 
  "OOP is fun! ";
}
}
class Welcome {
use 
  message1;
}
$obj = new Welcome();
$obj->msg1();
?>

Definition and Usage
The
trait
keyword is used to create traits. Traits are a way to allow classes to inherit
multiple behaviours.
